      "releaseNotes": "Create and connect in new ways. You can now add yourself and friends, and lip sync to your favorite songs or bring your vibe to life with custom dialogue.\nThe app also now supports the full suite of Meta AI glasses, including Ray-Ban Meta glasses, Oakley Meta Vanguard glasses, Meta Ray-Ban Display glasses and Meta Neural Band.\n \n*Certain Meta AI features are only available in select countries and languages. Some of these features may roll out slowly over time.",
      "version": "266.0.0",
      "wrapperType": "software",
      "currency": "USD",
      "description": "Create, remix, and share vibes—immersive AI videos of yourself, your friends, and anything you can imagine. Get tailored answers and inspiration with Meta AI, and go hands-free with AI glasses.\n \nGet access to industry-leading AI models for generating creative videos and images. Lip sync to your favorite songs with your friends or bring your vibes to life with custom dialogue. Just describe what you want to create and play with different edits and styles to make the perfect vibe. Explore the feed for inspiration from other AI creators, and instantly remix their vibes to add your own unique spin.\n \nNeed quick answers and recommendations? Talk to Meta AI through voice or text to get personal AI assistance throughout your day. And pair your AI glasses to go hands-free. The Meta AI app is the required companion app for managing your Meta AI glasses, importing and sharing media and more.\n \n*Certain Meta AI features are only available in select countries and languages. Some of these features may roll out slowly over time.\n \nNeed to report an issue or share feedback? Simply shake your phone and tap on “Submit a report”.",
